Second Department,

May, 1960

(May 2, 1960) William Coty et al., Appellants, v. Gerald O. Kaye et al., Respondents.

Motion referred to the court that rendered the decision. Nolan, P. J., Beldock, Ughetta, Kleinfeld and Christ, JJ., concur. Motion for reargument denied, without costs. Nolan, P. J., Ughetta, Kleinfeld, Pette and Brennan, JJ., concur.
